{"tid":107380,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"女學神撞石壆四輪朝天 師傅：真係反應唔到","createTime":"2017-02-04T12:34:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T12:56:46.000Z","uid":78819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e0a60be6b218f3264d43c70b517973261b22f042","tid":107380,"uid":78819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T12:34:42.000Z","msg":"下午4時許，一名24歲女學神沿荃灣青山公路進行駕駛練習，駛至大窩口支路時，懷疑猶豫不決，失控撞向路中石壆後向右翻側，教車師傅與女學神一度被困，其後自行爬出車廂。女學神手腳受傷需要送院治理，姓馬的教車師傅表示由於事出突然，坦言「一秒鐘嘅時間真係反應唔到」，所以來不及煞車而釀成意外。<br />\n<a href=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170204/280pix/1486200544_10bf.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170204%2F280pix%2F1486200544_10bf.jpg&d=WP5iSE3nEMa4dMETfl%2FD19tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=fc17d01a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170204/280pix/1486200544_10bf.jpg</a><br />\n私家車四輪朝天。（詹家志攝）<br />\n<a href=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170204/280pix/1486200545_f977.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170204%2F280pix%2F1486200545_f977.jpg&d=WP5iSE3nEMa4dMETfl%2FD19tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=e3cf74c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170204/280pix/1486200545_f977.jpg</a><br />\n女學神腳部受傷，經救護員包紮後送院治理。（詹家志攝）<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170204&amp;guid=56261635&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170204%26guid%3D56261635%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=WP5iSE3nEMa4dMETfl%2FD19tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=0c5082f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170204%26guid%3D56261635%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=b7122860\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170204&amp;guid=56261635&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n女人揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a923f3ed485dd574dd3ef1a41a73a9289e8064","tid":107380,"uid":25582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T12:42:18.000Z","msg":"師傅洗唔洗釘牌？"},{"pid":"c02a3e40b9a06c3df4d4c9da55ed05306726ce05","tid":107380,"uid":23785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T12:49:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>師傅洗唔洗釘牌？</blockquote><br />\n要，車都無埋"},{"pid":"22aad78c6899b646bc7420bc5f78fc498da559ca","tid":107380,"uid":78819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T12:56:46.000Z","msg":"唔好害人啦好心佢"}]}